This is a Houdini's Soho module for Mitsuba phisicaly based renderer:
http://www.mitsuba-renderer.org

@misc{Mitsuba,
   Author = {Wenzel Jakob},
   Year = {2010},
   Note = {http://www.mitsuba-renderer.org},
   Title = {Mitsuba renderer}
}

It is currently very basic, and I won't promise it will go much further.
Main purpose was to test some hair/cloth rendering archtecture in Mitsuba.
